{"tid":1434322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞清楚! 唔關割唔割事. 而係有D野根本唔應該做","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:46:27.000Z","uid":84267,"like":188,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8202e8c2c0866515aff7a38dc331b045618e729c","tid":1434322,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"不割席唔代表可以合理化所有無腦行為<br />\n例如衝機場禁區, 噴鐘樓<br />\n根本就壞事黎<br />\n已經做左就無辦法<br />\n但開始有人講會衝機場禁區, 好似搞到因為我地核爆都唔割所以做乜撚野都係啱咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好濫用不割席黎合理化所有行為<br />\n每件事諗清楚可行性, 成本效益同後果</span></span>"},{"pid":"939cee8ae4f73d3cc285a739f550fd0e040796e7","tid":1434322,"uid":179402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=7b8367f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=776ab9a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n有youtube喇！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"b29be37c8037295d21999e4c30f8f8554a260ffd","tid":1434322,"uid":270398,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:52:01.000Z","msg":"係咁推人去衝禁區既好明顯係打手黎<br />\n<br />\n今日班友又用番成日用既手法, 一面派人係咁引我地互屌/割席/打稻草人拆大台(實際上而家泛民根本就無意再搞大台, 因為佢地自己上一次搞完都無好下場), 仲有D人好陰濕咁突登提番5年前係死係左膠度所以而家都要再捉鬼(無錯5年前係死係左膠度, 但今次到而家佢地都無咩大動作, 根本唔需要突然SPIN去屌佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n另一方面就好似你咁講, 係度濫用不割席原則係咁叫人去做D 白撚痴兼送死既舉動仲要用不割席做擋箭牌唔俾你屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家共狗真係開始全力發動網軍攻打緊呢度, 大家醒水"},{"pid":"141838c6608cbf0dd6619d19c0cc73e0c873617d","tid":1434322,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"49ca79bce2431c83f4e79f8c54ea00b8765897a2","tid":1434322,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576e34d585b7aac58c37afa9af1de0ca16d8b3e6","tid":1434322,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:55:04.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c49b29a87cee550b40be58f03b3c16c57ea4fe02","tid":1434322,"uid":189157,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"鐘樓單野on9左<br />\n但係都唔會割<br />\n因為佢始終係我地既手足<br />\n其他人引以為鑑就得"},{"pid":"6df5ef54cc10e8e314980e706e5923d774227fbf","tid":1434322,"uid":277560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"用下個腦先行動呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39bae8f6b9e1cdcb87164a9336a5522e66c20f2","tid":1434322,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:57:59.000Z","msg":"唔割呀屌你老母<br />\n咪再玩分化<br />\n而家唔做都做左<br />\n我個人立場係覺得唔啱架啦<br />\n但都要出力spin 走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7554240cebbe802b67e209359b65765a7d1319ef","tid":1434322,"uid":250951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:58:02.000Z","msg":"希望大家明白翻不割背後都係要謹慎行事既道理"},{"pid":"2edf17e08bbf99adcbc103efec4d1cd061aee825","tid":1434322,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8202e8c2c0866515aff7a38dc331b045618e729c","tid":1434322,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"不割席唔代表可以合理化所有無腦行為<br />\n例如衝機場禁區, 噴鐘樓<br />\n根本就壞事黎<br />\n已經做左就無辦法<br />\n但開始有人講會衝機場禁區, 好似搞到因為我地核爆都唔割所以做乜撚野都係啱咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"